thread.title: Michael

author: Michael
title: Michael
text: I was completely satisfied. However, in future I think that flatmates needs to take into account Sydney Harbor. Often I was forwarded names of people who were looking for suburbs south of Sydney Harbor. As Sydney is very much a north of the Bridge/south of the Bridge sort of place, I wonder if it is of any use being sent people who list suburbs south of the Bridge,
